column5: ~~~Got out on Lady Simcoe on Sunday, blue sky, light winds, calm lake, time to go Perchen, weeeeeell seemed like a great idea, hit all my usaul spots and only caught 3 about this size, Pic from a past phishen trip  ~~~OOOOOOH well there's all ways next weekend
lol!! At least you were fishing.
On one of my tool boxes,the red sticker says it perfectly. "bad day of fishing is better than a good day at work". Works for me.!! Although a bit more work right now would be good lol.
